@Hugh_Jass wrote:

Honestly, I think it’s a bit sore on the eyes. You should try to learn a bit of grammar. And I agree with Ruby; pictures would be nice. I don’t want to join a site that has a bunch of viruses and such. Just calling it “The best RSPS ever” doesn’t make people want to play. It rather makes them want to believe you, but they have a hint of doubt.

Good luck with your server, though!
